<p>Data from the UK Biobank and the Brazilian Longitudinal Study of Adult Health are available for research to licensed users. Individual-level data for the Yale New Haven Health System cannot be made available due to HIPAA regulations enforced by the Yale IRB. The model is publicly accessible for research use on our website and programming code for generating key results is available from the authors on request.</p></section></section></section></section></article>

                      

